{"tid":1867194,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】經深圳灣口岸湧港現人潮 防暴警關外戒備","createTime":"2020-02-07T05:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T15:30:42.000Z","uid":34626,"like":109,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"a1748154aaa14f539e690491a468ed48567ed58f","tid":1867194,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:35:21.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎持續惡化蔓延下，特首林鄭未有聽取民意全面封關，更容許內地抵港人士明日凌晨才強制接受檢疫，造成昨日及今日的空窗期，由內地湧港人士勢必大增，今晨《蘋果》直擊其中一個仍可出入境的深圳灣口岸，發現深圳灣聯檢大樓有大批人士準備過關來港，旅遊巴大排長龍，在過境香港口岸有大批防暴警戒備，現場所見至少有四部警車，兩至三部警察私家車駐守。<br />\n<br />\n在深圳灣聯檢大樓，由深圳行往香港關口的旅客，目測亦有數百人，人頭湧湧，拖男帶女，旅客大包小包，有些甚至拖篋而行。排隊上巴士出香港市區的人龍亦絡繹不絕。至於中港車通道，記者目測車流較昨日疏落。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TUZ7Hj6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTUZ7Hj6.jpg&h=af238e5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RDOPVE6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDOPVE6.jpg&h=b70b5fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uXLyCTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuXLyCTs.jpg&h=a0112141&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加已經係社區爆發臨介點 <br />\n大家出少少力幫手啦好冇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三罷遊行開花 撐醫護封關</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解醫護罷得咁辛苦 冇人諗搞遊行支持佢地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1867017\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1867017</a>"},{"pid":"e664c57ef00f7c81a1825a863a274103a8cc7f9a","tid":1867194,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:35:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dad212e5f8cbe855cc24d45ebc94f1879e37272","tid":1867194,"uid":23340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d399e7d5592c2d032c4d05773a3f359bd381e7","tid":1867194,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:36:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":